    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) and <strong>sweet potato[es] </strong>(skins on)<strong> </strong>into thin chips, then add them to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
