    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>apple[s] </strong>and discard the core[s]</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Finely dice <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>onion</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining onion</strong> finely</p>",
