    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>pork mixture</strong> into 1 <strong>lean</strong> <strong>pork</strong> <strong>patty </strong>per person</p><p>Top the middle of <strong>pork</strong> <strong>patty[ies]</strong> with 4 pieces of<strong> cheddar </strong>and seal them in with the pork (make sure there are no gaps) – this your <strong>cheddar-stuffed pork patty[ies]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cheddar-stuffed pork patty[ies]</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) lightly covered in <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
