      "instruction": "<p>Add a dollop of <strong>tomato ketchup</strong> to these <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>ciabatta base</strong></p><p>Top with a <strong>cheddar-stuffed pork patty</strong>, a spoonful of the <strong>toffee apple & caramelised onion jam </strong>and the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>toffee apple, pork & cheddar burger</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> crispy kale</strong> and <strong>chips</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
